7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How to Conduct an ISO 17025 Management Reviews?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:59+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"what is management review (MR) as well as its significance and value. It will give you some practical advice on how to conduct a management review and"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to Conduct an ISO 17025 Management Reviews?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Since integrating ISO 17025into its management system, testing or calibration laboratory enters the maintenance and monitoring phase. This is not a dormant phase of operation, but rather a dynamic phase in which processes are monitored and trends are reviewed. It is now time to review the system during this \"live\" operational phase."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"There are steps in documenting management review following ISO 17025"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Document the ISO 17025 mandatory input review items."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Keep a record of who owns the process."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Make a list of the materials needed for the review."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Take note of the decision and action output record."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This article will help you understand what management review (MR) is, as well as its significance and value. It will give you some practical advice on how to conduct a management review and structure your documents to meet the requirements of ISO 17025."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"What is ISO 17025 management review?"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"A management review is not an audit or a report-back meeting. It is not about reporting metrics, but about determining how well the management system performs its functions and achieves its objectives. A management review is an opportunity for strategic planning. The goal of a management review is for top management and personnel involved in decision-making processes to evaluate the overall performance of the laboratory and it’s Quality Management System in a systematic manner."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Read on to find out more about how to Get ISO 17025 Certification in Dubai:"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 17025 Certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Why is it necessary to conduct management reviews?"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Organizations and stakeholders (including the accreditation body) must be assured of the laboratory's management system's ongoing suitability, adequacy, and effectiveness, as well as its stated policies and objectives. When flaws are identified through management review, plans can be made for necessary changes and resources."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22"]}],"$L23"]}]}]
